* making and publishing recording about a person in our home or in public space should be free without the consent of the recorded person
* principle:
	* what human eye is allowed to see  - let the   camera   be allowed to record too
	* what human ear is allowed to hear - let the microphone be allowed to record too
	* ...
* about the work of state agents too
	* this is harmless tool and usually the only one to uncover and defend against abuses of official power, corruption, unnecessary police brutality, false police allegations
